Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:46.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悄悄隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:54.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}讓飛雪滑過臉頰…
