Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:20.56,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}揺れる水面　その深くに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:24.22,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}青い宇宙映ってたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:27.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未来…そしてまた散っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}季節覚えている？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:39.44,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私たちは運命紡ぎながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:44.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その糸がどこまで続いてくのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.49,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}知らないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:49.42,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(ただそこに)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.61,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}inspiration　喜びとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.27,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}言葉を分かち合うたび
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.08,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ああいつか終わりの日が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.84,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そう感じさせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:07.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}initialize　その扉を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.36,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}開ける時が来るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}綺麗な時を閉じ込めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.93,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}湖に沈めたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.71,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけど私平気だよと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:28.35,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}星の便りに綴る
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:20.56,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在漣漪的水面深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:24.22,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}照映著蔚藍的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:27.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未來又將飄零而去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}唯此季節長存心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:39.44,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們編織命運之絲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:44.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}卻從來都不曾知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.49,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這絲線將通向何處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:49.42,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(僅僅佇立於此)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.61,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}每當我與他人分享
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.27,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}靈感乍現時的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.08,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就已經隱約察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.84,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終會有結束的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:07.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}重置人生的那扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.36,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終有漸漸打開之時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}美好時光關入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}再慢慢地沉入湖底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.71,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不過我會在星星上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:28.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}寫下一句「我沒事」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星雨這種東西  自從飛碟來了後就再沒見過了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.23,0:00:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使能看見  也要等上半個月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戶川同學一直在等待著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從七年前的那天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家拜託了  一起參加北美祭吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:04.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\pos(406,270)}「她所相信的東西」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  水坂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要參加北美祭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要做留學的準備嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.18,0:02:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一些擺脫不了的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  待會兒有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些話想對妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ok  ok
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便就行啦  接下來的就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預算到手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後參加者的名單裡  把汐音也寫了進去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是參加北美祭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們五個人一起參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話跟我說  指的是這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年級學生是不強制參加的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼趁人齊一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  戶川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直都是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是用來做什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是貼冰箱上的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急急忙忙把我拉過來  到底是想要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是個麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是因為你妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是柚季  提議的是古宮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戶川應該是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們不是一直很要好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直有種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誘因什麼的  會不會是點很無聊的小事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連要做什麼都不知道  怎麼可能找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也是古宮一個人找回來的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星象儀
