Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才要開始的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天已經很晚了  明天再開始做吧
